org.apache.drill.test.rowSet.file

Class JsonFileBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.rowSet.file.JsonFileBuilder

  • public class JsonFileBuilder
extends Object

    Overview

    Builds a json file containing the data in a RowSet.

    Example

    You can find an example of how to use JsonFileBuilder at ExampleTest.secondTest().
